                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<div class="rl-wave-sep rl-wave-sep-main-alt" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 52" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <path class="rl-wave-path" d="M0,0 C240,44 480,44 720,22 C960,0 1200,0 1440,30 L1440,52 L0,52 Z"></path>
    </svg>
</div>

<!-- ── Why Pawdopt ────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="rl-why">
    <div class="adopt-pg-container">
        <h2 class="rl-sec-title" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:2rem" data-i18n="rl-why-title">Why rehome through Pawdopt?</h2>
        <div class="rl-why-grid">
            <div class="rl-why-card">
                <span class="rl-why-icon">🔒</span>
                <h4 class="rl-why-ctitle" data-i18n="rl-why-c1">Safe &amp; private</h4>
                <p class="rl-why-cdesc" data-i18n="rl-why-c1d">Your address is never shown publicly. Only your city and province appear on your listing.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rl-why-card">
                <span class="rl-why-icon">💬</span>
                <h4 class="rl-why-ctitle" data-i18n="rl-why-c3">Direct contact</h4>
                <p class="rl-why-cdesc" data-i18n="rl-why-c3d">Talk to adopters before deciding. Read their profiles and ask as many questions as you need.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="rl-why-card">
                <span class="rl-why-icon">🐾</span>
                <h4 class="rl-why-ctitle" data-i18n="rl-why-c4">You stay in control</h4>
                <p class="rl-why-cdesc" data-i18n="rl-why-c4d">You choose who to meet. You decide the timing. You pick the family that feels right for your pet.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

